  "prompt": "What are the best web design firms in New York?",
  "response": "As of my last knowledge update in October 2023, several web design firms in New York are highly regarded for their creativity, technical expertise, and client satisfaction. While the \"best\" firm can depend on specific needs and preferences, here are some top web design firms in NYC:\n\n1. **Toptal** - Known for connecting businesses with top freelance developers and designers, Toptal has a pool of highly skilled professionals who can create custom websites tailored to specific needs.\n\n2. **Ruckus Marketing** - This agency specializes in branding, web design, and digital marketing. They focus on delivering high-quality and custom solutions for businesses.\n\n3. **Blue Fountain Media** - A full-service digital agency that offers web design, branding, and digital marketing services. They work with a variety of industries and are known for their innovative solutions.\n\n4. **Frog Design** - A leader in design and strategy, Frog Design combines innovation and technology to create impactful digital experiences. They focus on user-centric designs.\n\n5. **ThoughtBot** - A design and development firm specializing in creating web and mobile applications. They are known for their user-focused design process and work with startups and established companies alike.\n\n6. **Baked Creative** - This agency offers web design, branding, and various marketing services, focusing on building strong brand identities and user experiences.\n\n7. **Viget** - A digital agency offering web design, development, and marketing services. They emphasize collaboration and user-centered design.\n\n8. **Huge** - A global agency that specializes in digital marketing, web design, and user experience. Huge is known for working with large brands and creating influential digital products.\n\n9. **S10** - Focused on building high-quality websites and digital experiences, S10 is known for its collaborative approach and attention to detail.\n\n10. **The Future Forward** - A full-service agency that specializes in web design, branding, and digital marketing for various clients ranging from startups to established brands.\n\nWhen selecting a web design firm, it's important to consider your specific needs, budget, and the firm's portfolio to ensure they are the right fit for your project. Additionally, reading client testimonials and asking for case studies can provide insight into their capabilities and approach.",
